00:45:49.060 --> 00:45:53.120
globalization and getting your
app for a global audience

00:45:53.120 --> 00:45:54.340
makes lot of sense.

00:45:54.340 --> 00:45:58.740
We also looked at what it
entails and how do we achieve

00:45:58.740 --> 00:46:00.690
that in terms of both
internationalization and

00:46:00.690 --> 00:46:02.110
localization.

00:46:02.110 --> 00:46:03.850
We looked at available tools.

00:46:03.850 --> 00:46:05.520
Now, let's say you have
done all of that.

00:46:05.520 --> 00:46:07.250
You have now a localized app.

00:46:07.250 --> 00:46:09.170
What's next?

00:46:09.170 --> 00:46:12.660
The natural question is how
do I get my app now

00:46:12.660 --> 00:46:13.550
to the right audience?

00:46:13.550 --> 00:46:15.520
So how do I find the customers,
and do the global

00:46:15.520 --> 00:46:17.660
customers find me?

00:46:17.660 --> 00:46:21.140
So listed here are some of the
practical tips for you to

00:46:21.140 --> 00:46:25.160
market your app, especially
where is Google marketplaces,

00:46:25.160 --> 00:46:28.120
including Chrome web store,
including Google Play for

00:46:28.120 --> 00:46:29.860
Android app as well.

00:46:29.860 --> 00:46:32.940
So first and foremost, if you
do nothing else, you should

00:46:32.940 --> 00:46:36.540
localize your marketplace
metadata

00:46:36.540 --> 00:46:38.080
into different languages.

00:46:38.080 --> 00:46:42.930
That by itself significantly
boosts your app's ranking in

00:46:42.930 --> 00:46:46.840
the marketplace, especially
for that locale.

00:46:46.840 --> 00:46:48.590
So that's the first
and foremost part.

00:46:48.590 --> 00:46:51.110
The second is maximize your
search potential.

00:46:51.110 --> 00:46:52.250
Why is that important?

00:46:52.250 --> 00:46:58.670
Because search accounts for
about 2/3 of all installs and

00:46:58.670 --> 00:47:00.690
sales on Google Play.

00:47:00.690 --> 00:47:01.590
How do you do that?

00:47:01.590 --> 00:47:03.360
How do you maximize your
search potential?

00:47:03.360 --> 00:47:04.230
Think of the keywords.

00:47:04.230 --> 00:47:06.920
Think of the keywords that
somebody would search for when

00:47:06.920 --> 00:47:10.920
your app should show up and
include those in your title,

00:47:10.920 --> 00:47:12.630
in your description.

00:47:12.630 --> 00:47:14.980
Both of these fields are
indexed from a search

00:47:14.980 --> 00:47:15.760
perspective.

00:47:15.760 --> 00:47:18.540
And once you have included
those keywords in the

00:47:18.540 --> 00:47:22.140
respective locales as well, the
findability of your app

00:47:22.140 --> 00:47:27.270
increases multi-folds in terms
of a search perspective.

00:47:27.270 --> 00:47:30.950
One key insight in terms of,
again, ranking of your app in

00:47:30.950 --> 00:47:33.140
these locale, there are
three main factors

00:47:33.140 --> 00:47:33.990
that go into that.

00:47:33.990 --> 00:47:37.180
One is high number
of installs.

00:47:37.180 --> 00:47:39.650
The second is low number
of uninstalls.

00:47:39.650 --> 00:47:41.250
And the third is long
term usage.

00:47:41.250 --> 00:47:43.414
So how many users are using
your app over a

00:47:43.414 --> 00:47:44.590
long period of time?

00:47:44.590 --> 00:47:47.500
So for that, the steady effort
on your part for

00:47:47.500 --> 00:47:49.870
internationalization and
localization becomes a very

00:47:49.870 --> 00:47:51.190
key factor here.

00:47:51.190 --> 00:47:54.680
So think of your investment in
terms of advertising campaign

00:47:54.680 --> 00:47:58.680
and so on over a period of time
rather than just be in

00:47:58.680 --> 00:48:00.750
short bursts.

00:48:00.750 --> 00:48:04.620
And lastly, localize
your app listing.

00:48:04.620 --> 00:48:06.940
Localize your app screenshots.

00:48:06.940 --> 00:48:11.090
If your apps screenshot reflect
the actual user

00:48:11.090 --> 00:48:14.540
experience, the number of
the installs go higher.

00:48:14.540 --> 00:48:17.510
And more importantly, number
of uninstalls go lower.

00:48:17.510 --> 00:48:23.240
And that again helps in terms of
findability of your app on

00:48:23.240 --> 00:48:24.490
various marketplaces.

00:48:26.740 --> 00:48:28.750
So take home message.

00:48:28.750 --> 00:48:30.700
Important thing to
note here is--

00:48:30.700 --> 00:48:32.810
like again, we covered a
lot of details here.

00:48:32.810 --> 00:48:35.170
If you forget most of the stuff,
please remember these

00:48:35.170 --> 00:48:35.960
four things.

00:48:35.960 --> 00:48:38.200
First is it is never
too late to start.

00:48:38.200 --> 00:48:40.820
So if you haven't done that, you
still have your app only

00:48:40.820 --> 00:48:44.510
in English or one of the
languages, get started now.

00:48:44.510 --> 00:48:46.430
Get started today.

00:48:46.430 --> 00:48:49.950
Opportunity, as we have showed
in the initial slide,

00:48:49.950 --> 00:48:51.840
opportunity is just too
big for you to ignore.

00:48:51.840 --> 00:48:53.800
So focus on that.

00:48:53.800 --> 00:48:57.050
The third is it is relatively
very simple to get started.

00:48:57.050 --> 00:48:59.940
And again, it will not get you
in the perfect state right

00:48:59.940 --> 00:49:01.370
away, but you will get there.

00:49:01.370 --> 00:49:04.180
So things like just remove
any hard-coded string.

00:49:04.180 --> 00:49:04.610
Externalize them.

00:49:04.610 --> 00:49:08.980
Make them as resource bundles
and send them for translation.

00:49:08.980 --> 00:49:12.500
Use a few libraries so that
you do the number handling

00:49:12.500 --> 00:49:15.740
date format, currency formats,
et cetera, correctly.

00:49:15.740 --> 00:49:19.300
And then, get your friend, get
your family to come and help

00:49:19.300 --> 00:49:20.910
you translate in just
one language.

00:49:20.910 --> 00:49:23.110
So you can essentially take all
your strings and say, OK,

00:49:23.110 --> 00:49:23.740
we're good to go.

00:49:23.740 --> 00:49:25.340
Let's essentially use
these and just

00:49:25.340 --> 00:49:26.700
do it for one language.

00:49:26.700 --> 00:49:28.020
It will not be perfect
as I said.

00:49:28.020 --> 00:49:30.270
But it will put you in
the right direction

00:49:30.270 --> 00:49:32.870
on the right path.

